[SHIRLEY'S MOM cries]
No!

61
00:05:18,458 --> 00:05:20,625
[KANON] I see.
She was a friend of yours.

62
00:05:20,708 --> 00:05:23,333
[NINA] Yes. Milly just
told me about it.

63
00:05:23,416 --> 00:05:25,250
[KANON]
Were you close?

64
00:05:25,333 --> 00:05:28,750
[NINA] I'm not sure. She was
just always so cheerful.

65
00:05:28,833 --> 00:05:31,625
To be honest,
she kind of bothered me.

66
00:05:31,708 --> 00:05:34,541
[KANON] I see. Perhaps you were
envious of her happiness?

67
00:05:34,625 --> 00:05:39,250
[NINA] Maybe Maybe that
was it. That's why...

68
00:05:39,333 --> 00:05:42,416
I never imagined that
I would cry over her!

69
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:45,750
[KANON] Nina as long
as you can shed tears,

70
00:05:45,833 --> 00:05:47,375
then you're all right.

71
00:05:50,625 --> 00:05:53,833
[C.C.] I can't believe Lelouch.
Who does he think I am?

72
00:05:53,916 --> 00:05:55,333
Leaving me behind here

73
00:05:55,416 --> 00:05:58,250
like I was a messenger
girl or something.

74
00:06:00,541 --> 00:06:02,375
[C.C.]
What?! Ugh, hardly.

75
00:06:02,458 --> 00:06:05,375
I'm just really worried that
he's forgotten our contract.

76
00:06:05,458 --> 00:06:07,416
Anyway, what are you
planning to do?

77
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:10,083
How long are you going
to stay inside of--

78
00:06:10,166 --> 00:06:11,166
C.C.

79
00:06:11,250 --> 00:06:12,541
[C.C.]
Hm?

80
00:06:12,625 --> 00:06:14,250
[LELOUCH] I have finally
located where the Order is.

81
00:06:14,333 --> 00:06:16,666
Jeremiah and Rolo provided
key information.

82
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:19,500
We're going to send in the
Zero Squad and wipe it out.

83
00:06:19,583 --> 00:06:22,625
[C.C.] Wipe it out?
Weren't you going to use it?

84
00:06:22,708 --> 00:06:24,416
They're not a military group.

85
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:26,125
They just do research
into Geass--

86
00:06:26,208 --> 00:06:27,666
We'll crush them!

87
00:06:28,708 --> 00:06:30,541
Tell me what happened.

88
00:06:37,583 --> 00:06:39,750
[LELOUCH] The power of
Geass which they unleashed

89
00:06:39,833 --> 00:06:43,416
