going to wipe out the Order?

91
00:06:46,125 --> 00:06:47,583
As atonement.

92
00:06:47,666 --> 00:06:49,708
To make sure the same thing
doesn't happen to anyone else.

93
00:06:49,791 --> 00:06:51,708
You said Geass is the
power of the king.

94
00:06:51,791 --> 00:06:54,750
There can be only one king,
so I alone shall have it.

95
00:06:54,833 --> 00:06:58,500
I will erase Rolo. I'll erase
Geass from all the others.

96
00:06:58,583 --> 00:07:00,750
Its power to make people
sinful will be obliterated

97
00:07:00,833 --> 00:07:02,041
from this world!

98
00:07:02,125 --> 00:07:05,041
