At the very least!

99
00:07:05,125 --> 00:07:07,208
And are you going to
erase me, as well?

100
00:07:07,291 --> 00:07:08,666
[LELOUCH]
You know I can't do that.

101
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:10,625
You are eternally young.
And immortal.

102
00:07:10,708 --> 00:07:13,958
V.V. is also eternally young.
And also immortal.

103
00:07:14,041 --> 00:07:16,291
I'll neutralize him
and leave him helpless.

104
00:07:16,375 --> 00:07:18,916
And there's always the method
that Clovis used on you.

105
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:22,458
Besides, I want to see if you're
really loyal to me now.

106
00:07:22,541 --> 00:07:25,541
Since you were once the leader
of the Order we're fighting.

107
00:07:25,625 --> 00:07:28,791
That was a long time ago.
And I was just window dressing.

108
00:07:28,875 --> 00:07:32,041
I never had real
power like V.V...

109
00:07:32,125 --> 00:07:34,208
Still.

110
00:07:34,291 --> 00:07:36,208
We've been accomplices,
haven't we?

111
00:07:36,291 --> 00:07:39,083
[LELOUCH] The order will be
wiped out which will test you.

112
00:07:39,166 --> 00:07:41,541
[C.C.] I'm prepared to
see it through to the end.

113
00:07:41,625 --> 00:07:43,833
[LELOUCH] Good, because
there's one thing more:

114
00:07:43,916 --> 00:07:45,875
I want to know the details
of our contract.

115
00:07:45,958 --> 00:07:48,000
What is it you want
from all this?

116
00:07:48,083 --> 00:07:50,000
[C.C.] That has nothing
to do with the mission;

117
00:07:50,083 --> 00:07:51,875
I have no intention
