00:07:51,958 --> 00:07:54,708
[LELOUCH]
Hmpf! Willful woman!

119
00:07:54,791 --> 00:07:58,875
Yes, that's right. That's
exactly what makes me C.C.

120
00:08:01,083 --> 00:08:02,916
[PRIEST B] Bartley and
the others are one thing,

121
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,458
but what do we do about
Princess Cornelia?

122
00:08:05,541 --> 00:08:08,541
[PRIEST C] Shouldn't we at
least contact His Majesty?

123
00:08:08,625 --> 00:08:13,166
[V.V.] Hm. I wonder if Charles
knew about Cornelia's actions.

124
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:14,916
Or if he didn't...

125
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:15,958
[PRIEST B]
Huh?

126
00:08:16,041 --> 00:08:17,250
[PA VOICE]
Director V.V., we have

127
00:08:17,333 --> 00:08:19,250
the scheduled transmission
from Lord Jeremiah.

128
00:08:19,333 --> 00:08:22,541
[V.V.] Right. Can you
patch it through?

129
00:08:22,625 --> 00:08:23,791
Surprised to see me?

130
00:08:23,875 --> 00:08:24,708
[V.V.]
Uh.

131
00:08:24,791 --> 00:08:26,708
[LELOUCH]
So, you're V.V...

132
00:08:26,791 --> 00:08:28,208
Lelouch!

133
00:08:28,291 --> 00:08:30,500
[PRIEST A] How can he have
access to Jeremiah's network?!

134
00:08:30,583 --> 00:08:31,916
[PRIEST D]
Where's the signal from?

135
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:34,916
[PRIEST C] Area 11. Looks
like he's inside Ashford.

136
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:37,500
[LELOUCH] I'm sure I need no
introduction at this point,

137
00:08:37,583 --> 00:08:39,750
so I'll just start with
direct questions.

138
00:08:39,833 --> 00:08:41,500
Was it you who
kidnapped Nunnally

139
00:08:41,583 --> 00:08:43,250
during the battle for Tokyo?

140
00:08:43,333 --> 00:08:46,041
Also, did you put Suzaku
and I and the others

141
00:08:46,125 --> 00:08:48,541
on Kamine Island to observe us?

142
00:08:48,625 --> 00:08:49,958
[V.V.]
Yes, that's correct.

143
00:08:50,041 --> 00:08:52,083
But the fact that you're
asking these questions

144
00:08:52,166 --> 00:08:54,833
means you've regained all of
your memories, doesn't it?

145
00:08:54,916 --> 00:08:56,958
That's right, I am Zero.

146
00:08:57,041 --> 00:09:00,291
[V.V.] Then C.C. must be with
you. Can you hand her over?

147
00:09:00,375 --> 00:09:02,041
We'll let you go free if you do.

148
00:09:02,125 --> 00:09:03,458
It's too late for that!

149
00:09:03,541 --> 00:09:06,125
I hereby declare war against
you, with no mercy!

150
00:09:06,208 --> 00:09:09,250
[V.V.] Oh yeah! But by the
time you get here from Area 11,

151
00:09:09,333 --> 00:09:11,458
we'll have moved
to another place--

152
00:09:11,541 --> 00:09:12,583
[explosion]

153
00:09:12,666 --> 00:09:14,541
[PA VOICE]
Director V.V.! Knightmares!

154
00:09:14,625 --> 00:09:15,625
What?!

155
00:09:15,708 --> 00:09:18,416
[PA GUY]
I think it's the Black Knights!

156
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:20,833
[C.C.] V.V.'s current
location is verified.

157
00:09:20,916 --> 00:09:23,791
Strike force,
encircle point alpha-7!

158
00:09:25,541 --> 00:09:27,750
[V.V.]
I see. So, that's how it is.

159
00:09:27,833 --> 00:09:31,000
That's right. I'm glad you
gave me a bit of your time.

160
00:09:31,083 --> 00:09:33,416
You just had to let down
your guard for a moment.

161
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:35,416
Since you believed
I was in Area 11,

162
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:37,125
you thought you had
time to escape.

163
00:09:37,208 --> 00:09:39,166
That's why you're
trapped now.

164
00:09:39,250 --> 00:09:43,541
V.V., the one who shall render
judgement here is me!

165
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,291
[ALL screaming]

166
00:09:54,916 --> 00:09:56,958
[V.V.] Load the research
data into the Eject Dart

167
00:09:57,041 --> 00:09:59,750
and prepare the device;
you know which one I mean.

168
00:09:59,833 --> 00:10:01,833
[PRIEST A] Director, you're
facing them personally?

169
00:10:01,916 --> 00:10:04,500
I need to buy you time
to escape with the data.

170
00:10:04,583 --> 00:10:09,041
Besides, I have to teach some
discipline to Marianne's child.

171
00:10:09,125 --> 00:10:11,041
I never would have guessed.

172
00:10:11,125 --> 00:10:13,916
