royal princess, Nunnally.

173
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,250
[NUNNALLY] Forgive me for
hiding things from you.

174
00:10:16,333 --> 00:10:18,250
[KALLEN]
Same for me.

175
00:10:18,333 --> 00:10:21,666
[NUNNALLY] It's so nostalgic,
talking about Ashford Academy.

176
00:10:21,750 --> 00:10:24,250
They told me I wouldn't
see Milly and the others.

177
00:10:24,333 --> 00:10:27,375
So Suzaku is the only one
I've been able to talk to.

178
00:10:27,458 --> 00:10:30,125
They also said my
brother has vanished.

179
00:10:30,208 --> 00:10:31,833
No one knows where he is.

180
00:10:31,916 --> 00:10:34,416
Tell me, what sort of brother
was Lelouch for you?

181
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:35,625
Huh?

182
00:10:35,708 --> 00:10:37,083
[KALLEN] I used to have
a brother, too, so,

183
00:10:37,166 --> 00:10:39,083
that's why I ask.

184
00:10:39,166 --> 00:10:40,708
[NUNNALLY] I'm happy
just to have someone

185
00:10:40,791 --> 00:10:42,625
to talk to about Lelouch.

186
00:10:44,583 --> 00:10:45,916
Excuse me, please.

187
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,125
[KALLEN]
Mm?

188
00:10:47,208 --> 00:10:48,375
[SUZAKU]
Viceroy Nunnally,

189
00:10:48,458 --> 00:10:51,541
I'd like to borrow prisoner
1-0-7 from you.

190
00:10:51,625 --> 00:10:52,416
[NUNNALLY]
Uh.

191
00:10:55,041 --> 00:10:56,750
[ALL screaming]

192
00:10:58,291 --> 00:11:00,875
[STAFF groaning]

193
00:11:02,083 --> 00:11:03,333
[BLACK KNIGHT A]
Sub-commander Kinoshita,

194
00:11:03,416 --> 00:11:04,708
something's wrong here!

195
00:11:04,791 --> 00:11:07,291
This isn't a Britannian
military installation.

196
00:11:07,375 --> 00:11:09,416
Uh. Yeah, you're right.

197
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:11,708
They haven't put up
any resistance at all.

198
00:11:11,791 --> 00:11:13,916
They don't even seem
to have weapons.

199
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,916
[ZERO]
Use extreme prejudice!

200
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,250
But, sir...!

201
00:11:17,333 --> 00:11:18,666
[ZERO] Britannia has
been colluding with traitors

202
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:20,041
in the Chinese Federation.

203
00:11:20,125 --> 00:11:21,916
This lab is developing
immortal warriors

204
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,875
whose purpose
is to destroy us!

205
00:11:23,958 --> 00:11:26,541
I won't let them violate
the sanctity of life!

206
00:11:26,625 --> 00:11:29,833
The researchers and their
data are to be wiped out!

207
00:11:29,916 --> 00:11:30,958
We don't know where the subjects

208
00:11:31,041 --> 00:11:32,958
