research are hidden!

209
00:11:33,041 --> 00:11:36,166
Therefore, encircle point
alpha-7 and destroy everything!

210
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:39,958
Burn it to the ground! Any
experimental subjects found

211
00:11:40,041 --> 00:11:43,375
are to be sealed inside
of high pressure casing!

212
00:11:43,458 --> 00:11:46,541
I will investigate each
one of them personally!

213
00:11:47,833 --> 00:11:50,250
[BARTLEY] Have you found
Princess Cornelia yet?!

214
00:11:50,333 --> 00:11:52,625
We have to use this
chance to save everyo--

215
00:11:52,708 --> 00:11:53,791
[ALL screaming]

216
00:11:57,541 --> 00:12:00,916
That man there, wasn't
he working with Clovis?

217
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,583
[STAFF A]
Director C.C.!

218
00:12:02,666 --> 00:12:04,333
You've come back to us!

219
00:12:04,416 --> 00:12:06,958
[STAFF B]
Please save us, C.C.!

220
00:12:07,041 --> 00:12:08,125
[C.C. gasps]

221
00:12:12,083 --> 00:12:14,333
Your Highness, Prince Clovis...

222
00:12:14,416 --> 00:12:17,791
The eternally young, immortal
woman you wished to present

223
00:12:17,875 --> 00:12:20,791
to His Majesty. It would
seem that he was already

224
00:12:20,875 --> 00:12:24,375
aware of her
existence. Please...

225
00:12:24,458 --> 00:12:26,458
Please forgive me,
Your Highness...

226
00:12:27,875 --> 00:12:31,375
We never should've involved
ourselves with that witch.

227
00:12:39,291 --> 00:12:40,625
[DIETHARD]
Yes,

228
00:12:40,708 --> 00:12:42,375
Zero's gone to attack a
Britannian research facility.

229
00:12:42,458 --> 00:12:44,916
He's kept the location
and mission secret.

230
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,958
More of those
clandestine activities?

231
00:12:47,041 --> 00:12:49,000
And now that the Saudis
have been subjugated

232
00:12:49,083 --> 00:12:52,250
