quickly as you say.

235
00:12:57,250 --> 00:12:58,916
[XING-KE] But there's positive
movement as well.

236
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:01,083
Italy and Poland have
come over to our side.

237
00:13:01,166 --> 00:13:04,000
We need to speak to Zero
as soon as he returns.

238
00:13:04,083 --> 00:13:05,500
[DIETHARD]
Understood.

239
00:13:06,833 --> 00:13:08,833
[DIETHARD] This is what
Zero wants, isn't it?

240
00:13:08,916 --> 00:13:11,083
Yes. We have to
maintain tight secrecy

241
00:13:11,166 --> 00:13:14,458
around his activities
and his very existence.

242
00:13:14,541 --> 00:13:17,208
[DIETHARD] Then I want you to go
after deputy-commander Ohgi.

243
00:13:17,291 --> 00:13:18,291
[SAYOKO]
Huh?

244
00:13:18,375 --> 00:13:19,541
[DIETHARD]
He's been acting strangely

245
00:13:19,625 --> 00:13:22,875
since the meeting a few
days ago. No. He's been

246
00:13:22,958 --> 00:13:26,416
hiding something from us
for a long time before that.

247
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:29,500
[AIRPORT STAFF sighs] Flights
to the Chinese Federation

248
00:13:29,583 --> 00:13:31,000
right now are cancelled...

249
00:13:31,083 --> 00:13:32,916
[VILLETTA] I belong to the
Office of Secret Intelligence.

250
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,333
[AIRPORT STAFF]
Th-he one that reports

251
00:13:34,416 --> 00:13:36,041
directly to His Majesty?!

252
00:13:36,125 --> 00:13:37,250
[VILLETTA]
Right. I believe you have

253
00:13:37,333 --> 00:13:39,833
special flights for
diplomatic purposes.

254
00:13:39,916 --> 00:13:42,083
[AIRPORT STAFF]
Yes ma'am we do.

255
00:13:42,166 --> 00:13:44,875
[VILLETTA] Now that Lelouch has
roped even Jermiah into this...

256
00:13:44,958 --> 00:13:47,166
For Zero's sake, if
the deputy-commander

257
00:13:47,250 --> 00:13:49,083
is collaborating with
the enemy, then...

258
00:13:49,166 --> 00:13:52,375
[VILLETTA]
I must kill Ohgi Kaname!

259
00:13:53,333 --> 00:13:54,375
[MORI]
Huh?

260
00:13:54,458 --> 00:13:56,458
What are children
doing here?

261
00:13:56,541 --> 00:13:58,375
Uh... Hm?

262
00:14:09,791 --> 00:14:11,416
What the...?!

263
00:14:13,125 --> 00:14:16,416
Ugh! My hand! [grunting]

264
00:14:19,375 --> 00:14:21,083
What the devil are
you doing, Mori?!

265
00:14:21,166 --> 00:14:23,541
It's not me!
I can't control it!

266
00:14:27,958 --> 00:14:29,166
Uh? It's Geass?

267
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:30,583
That power means it's...

268
00:14:30,666 --> 00:14:32,083
Big brother Rolo!

269
00:14:32,166 --> 00:14:35,208
Hey, I miss all you guys:
how have you been?

270
00:14:41,250 --> 00:14:44,250
The new guy.
Your name's Rolo, isn't it?

271
00:14:44,333 --> 00:14:46,166
Are you one of them?

272
00:14:47,083 --> 00:14:49,416
I have nothing to
do with them now.

273
00:14:49,500 --> 00:14:54,250
As long as I keep following
my brother, I'm all right.

274
00:14:54,333 --> 00:14:57,083
[LELOUCH laughs]
Once he corners V.V.,

275
00:14:57,166 --> 00:15:00,250
I'll simply detonate the bomb I
planted in Rolo's knightmare.

276
00:15:00,333 --> 00:15:03,125
My funeral offering to
Shirley will be Rolo's life!

277
00:15:03,208 --> 00:15:06,625
He will atone for
what he did to her!

278
00:15:06,708 --> 00:15:07,916
What?!

279
00:15:10,083 --> 00:15:11,041
The Siegfried!

280
00:15:11,125 --> 00:15:12,250
[JEREMIAH]
Impossible!

281
00:15:12,333 --> 00:15:13,958
[LELOUCH]
Jermiah! Isn't that unit...?!

282
00:15:14,041 --> 00:15:17,125
Yes. Since it works on
direct bio-connect...

283
00:15:17,208 --> 00:15:19,250
The only one who can
use it beside me is...!

284
00:15:19,333 --> 00:15:20,083
[V.V.]
Heh.

285
00:15:20,166 --> 00:15:21,208
[LELOUCH]
I thought so!

286
00:15:24,333 --> 00:15:26,125
You surprise me, V.V.!

287
00:15:27,208 --> 00:15:29,500
[LELOUCH] The observer
becomes the perpetrator!

288
00:15:29,583 --> 00:15:33,250
[V.V.] Y'know, I sort of
liked you, Lelouch.

289
00:15:33,333 --> 00:15:35,958
Because you reminded
me of Charles.

290
00:15:37,291 --> 00:15:38,291
[C.C.]
I can't believe it...

291
00:15:38,375 --> 00:15:40,291
He's using the
Siegfried unit here?!

292
00:15:40,375 --> 00:15:42,875
[LELOUCH] Get out of here!
You're the one he's after!

293
00:15:45,958 --> 00:15:46,958
[V.V.]
Oh?

294
00:15:47,041 --> 00:15:48,291
[JEREMIAH]
Hold it right there, V.V.!

295
00:15:48,375 --> 00:15:50,000
[ROLO]
Please, just surrender.

296
00:15:50,083 --> 00:15:51,375
Who do you think
you're talking to?

297
00:15:51,458 --> 00:15:53,291
You're just a bunch of
traitors, aren't you!

298
00:15:53,375 --> 00:15:56,500
V.V., I swear I'll tear you
out of that thing myself!

299
00:15:56,583 --> 00:15:58,208
All units: attack!

300
00:15:58,291 --> 00:16:00,708
Yes, Your Majesty!

301
00:16:03,541 --> 00:16:05,000
[laughs]

302
00:16:06,333 --> 00:16:09,083
[LELOUCH growls] That spinning
shield is powerful!

303
00:16:09,166 --> 00:16:12,333
Marianne's son is getting
carried away with himself!

304
00:16:15,666 --> 00:16:16,750
[JEREMIAH]
That machine

305
00:16:16,833 --> 00:16:18,666
was made so that I
could prove my loyalty!

306
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:22,208
Jeremiah, I thought that you had
a personal grudge against Zero?

307
00:16:22,291 --> 00:16:24,875
I did! Because I thought
he was a mere commoner

308
00:16:24,958 --> 00:16:27,333
preventing me from
serving the royal family.

309
00:16:27,416 --> 00:16:30,375
But now I know who he is, and I
know that by serving him...

310
00:16:30,458 --> 00:16:33,000
I am serving my lady, Marianne!

311
00:16:33,083 --> 00:16:34,333
[V.V.]
Even you...!

312
00:16:34,416 --> 00:16:36,916
You dare speak
her name to me!

313
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,791
[BLACK KNIGHT RADIO]
Send out all remaining units!

314
00:16:41,875 --> 00:16:43,208
It looks like that
monster outside

315
00:16:43,291 --> 00:16:45,125
is piloted by their leader!

316
00:16:48,416 --> 00:16:49,375
[KALLEN]
Shirley?!

317
00:16:49,458 --> 00:16:51,000
[SUZAKU]
According to the forensics,

318
00:16:51,083 --> 00:16:52,208
she committed suicide.

319
00:16:52,291 --> 00:16:53,541
[KALLEN]
She'd never do that!

320
00:16:53,625 --> 00:16:55,458
Suzaku, you know
that, don't you?!

321
00:16:55,541 --> 00:16:59,625
[SUZAKU] Yeah, I do. Which means
that if somebody murdered her...

322
00:16:59,708 --> 00:17:00,583
[gasps]

323
00:17:00,666 --> 00:17:03,083
[SUZAKU]
Yes. Lelouch...

324
00:17:03,166 --> 00:17:04,875
[LELOUCH grunts]

325
00:17:04,958 --> 00:17:07,833
[LELOUCH] Rolo! Can you get
to the Siegfried somehow?

326
00:17:07,916 --> 00:17:11,250
I'm not able to use my Geass
to do time stops on V.V...

327
00:17:11,333 --> 00:17:13,250
[LELOUCH] You just need
to grab onto the unit.

328
00:17:13,333 --> 00:17:14,541
I have a plan after that.

329
00:17:14,625 --> 00:17:17,291
Okay, I'll do my best.

330
00:17:17,375 --> 00:17:20,666
[LELOUCH] Rolo, the bomb I
planted on the Vincent is ready!

331
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:24,125
It'll destroy the Siegfried
and you in one blast.

332
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:27,166
[ROLO]
I have to try!

333
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:28,833
For big brother!

334
00:17:30,833 --> 00:17:32,375
And now it's Rolo's turn.

335
00:17:32,458 --> 00:17:35,291
You've lied to me just like
all the others, haven't you?

336
00:17:35,375 --> 00:17:38,625
Even knowing that your
Geass won't work on me...

337
00:17:43,458 --> 00:17:44,375
Oh, yeah!

338
00:17:44,458 --> 00:17:45,958
[PRIEST A]
Director V.V.,

339
00:17:46,041 --> 00:17:48,375
we've finished preparations to
escape with the research data.

340
00:17:48,458 --> 00:17:50,208
Shall we take it to
the E.U. for now?

341
00:17:50,291 --> 00:17:52,958
[V.V.] Yes. I'll join you after
I've finished things here.

342
00:17:53,041 --> 00:17:54,833
Now I know how to capture C.C.,

343
00:17:54,916 --> 00:17:57,333
so all we need to do
is escape and regroup,

344
00:17:57,416 --> 00:18:00,250
then Charles and I can put
an end to this for good.

345
00:18:01,666 --> 00:18:03,041
I just have to grab it!

346
00:18:03,125 --> 00:18:06,000
You are a failed experiment,
don't you know that?

347
00:18:06,083 --> 00:18:08,958
Your heart stops every
time you use your Geass.

348
00:18:09,041 --> 00:18:13,208
That means you're defective. You
could conk out at any moment.

349
00:18:14,875 --> 00:18:17,250
Not yet! If I eject them...!

350
00:18:17,583 --> 00:18:19,083
Oh, yeah!

351
00:18:19,541 --> 00:18:21,875
[ROLO]
I've done it, big brother!

352
00:18:21,958 --> 00:18:23,875
[screams]

353
00:18:23,958 --> 00:18:25,166
[V.V. laughs]

354
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:27,125
[LELOUCH]
Well done, Rolo!

355
00:18:27,208 --> 00:18:29,708
Now, it's time for goodbye!

356
00:18:33,291 --> 00:18:34,208
[LELOUCH grunts]

357
00:18:36,125 --> 00:18:40,333
[V.V.] Who? Who could know the
Siegfrieg's only weak point?

358
00:18:40,416 --> 00:18:41,708
[V.V. growls]

359
00:18:46,750 --> 00:18:49,541
So, your name is V.V.?
You were mistaken

360
00:18:49,625 --> 00:18:52,041
when you treated me like
an incompetent weakling.

361
00:18:52,125 --> 00:18:52,958
[ROLO gasps]

362
00:18:53,041 --> 00:18:55,375
[ROLO]
Forgive me, Big Brother!

363
00:18:55,458 --> 00:18:57,541
[LELOUCH]
No, it's all right.

364
00:18:57,625 --> 00:19:00,875
[LELOUCH] I never expected
Cornelia to be here!

365
00:19:00,958 --> 00:19:04,416
The Siegfried's shields are
all down! Direct attack!

366
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:06,250
[V.V.]
Uh... Uh!

367
00:19:06,333 --> 00:19:09,958
Now you're going to suffer,
for what you did to Euphy!

368
00:19:10,041 --> 00:19:10,958
The source...

369
00:19:11,041 --> 00:19:12,625
[LELOUCH, CORNELIA]
...of Geass!

370
00:19:16,375 --> 00:19:18,708
[V.V.] It's no use! The
Siegfried is finished!

371
00:19:18,791 --> 00:19:20,125
Uh!

372
00:19:23,625 --> 00:19:27,250
It's you, Lelouch!
You are an abomination!

373
00:19:27,791 --> 00:19:29,041
[JEREMIAH]
Come, Your Highness!

374
00:19:34,166 --> 00:19:35,375
[PRIEST A]
The Siegfried!

375
00:19:35,458 --> 00:19:36,958
[PRIEST B]
Director V.V.!

376
00:19:37,041 --> 00:19:41,125
[PRIEST C] Calm down! Remember,
director V.V. cannot be killed.

377
00:19:41,208 --> 00:19:44,083
He can always use the Twilight
Gate on the lowest level.

378
00:19:44,166 --> 00:19:47,958
If we just get the research data
away from here, then we...

379
00:19:48,041 --> 00:19:48,750
[PRIEST A]
Ah!

380
00:19:48,833 --> 00:19:49,583
[PRIEST B]
Is that...?!

381
00:19:49,666 --> 00:19:51,791
[PRIEST C]
Huh?! Lady C.C.!

382
00:19:52,583 --> 00:19:53,833
[C.C.]
Forgive me.

383
00:19:53,916 --> 00:19:57,041
This is my personal sin
for having neglected you.

384
00:19:57,125 --> 00:20:00,583
At last I shall put an end
to the lineage of Geass.

385
00:20:00,666 --> 00:20:04,750
So be it. Perhaps, this is
how Lelouch and I should...

386
00:20:09,208 --> 00:20:11,541
[SUZAKU] All of the evidence
and testimony imply

387
00:20:11,625 --> 00:20:16,666
that Lelouch is innocent...
But in my heart, I've known

388
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:19,958
all along that Lelouch was the
culprit. That he was Zero.

389
00:20:20,041 --> 00:20:21,625
[KALLEN]
I don't know who Zero is!

390
00:20:21,708 --> 00:20:23,625
I told you that when
I was captured.

391
00:20:23,708 --> 00:20:24,958
[SUZAKU]
Enough of that!

392
00:20:25,041 --> 00:20:28,000
To prevent another
death like Shirley's...

393
00:20:28,083 --> 00:20:30,625
Nothing is off limits;
not anymore!

394
00:20:30,708 --> 00:20:32,958
And that includes Refrain.

395
00:20:33,041 --> 00:20:34,125
[KALLEN gasps]

396
00:20:34,208 --> 00:20:36,250
[LELOUCH]
The target has fled inside!

397
00:20:36,333 --> 00:20:38,500
I'll look for him, starting
on the lowest level!

398
00:20:38,583 --> 00:20:41,708
Rolo, you search from
the top down! Kinoshita!

399
00:20:41,791 --> 00:20:44,541
Take command and sweep
the middle levels!

400
00:20:44,625 --> 00:20:47,458
[V.V. sighs, groans]

401
00:20:47,541 --> 00:20:50,666
Lelouch How dare you!

402
00:20:58,708 --> 00:21:01,958
I'm glad you came
after all... Charles.

403
00:21:02,041 --> 00:21:04,375
The most splendid
relationship in the world

404
00:21:04,458 --> 00:21:06,291
is that of loyal siblings.

405
00:21:06,375 --> 00:21:08,250
[EMPEROR]
Big brother, is it true

406
00:21:08,333 --> 00:21:11,208
you were the one who sent
an assassin after Lelouch?

407
00:21:11,291 --> 00:21:13,000
[V.V.]
Yes. And thanks to that,

408
00:21:13,083 --> 00:21:15,708
I've been the victim
of his assassins.

409
00:21:15,791 --> 00:21:19,666
But I've also learned something.
That Lelouch is Zero.

410
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:22,166
That he even tricked Nunnally.

411
00:21:22,250 --> 00:21:26,541
You lied to me once
again, big brother.

412
00:21:26,625 --> 00:21:29,333
[KINOSHITA] This is as barbaric
as the Britannians!

413
00:21:29,416 --> 00:21:33,291
Was it really necessary to
shoot children? Was it?

414
00:21:36,416 --> 00:21:38,458
I'm picking up signs of life.

415
00:21:38,541 --> 00:21:44,500
Have you returned to the
point where you began? V.V.!

416
00:21:44,583 --> 00:21:46,375
What's this?! Dammit!

417
00:21:46,458 --> 00:21:48,708
This is what happened
on Kamine Island!

418
00:21:53,875 --> 00:21:56,625
[gasps] How was I pulled
out of the Shinkiro?

419
00:21:56,708 --> 00:22:00,750
Where is this place? It's not
an illusion or a hologram.

420
00:22:00,833 --> 00:22:02,208
[EMPEROR]
That is correct!

421
00:22:02,291 --> 00:22:03,625
[LELOUCH gasps]

422
00:22:03,708 --> 00:22:05,625
[EMPEROR] And knight mares
are such inelegant things.

423
00:22:05,708 --> 00:22:10,375
Especially in the face of this
system: the Sword of Akasha!

424
00:22:10,458 --> 00:22:12,583
[gasps] It's you...!

425
00:22:12,666 --> 00:22:16,708
[EMPEROR] Lelouch, my son!
The time has come at last!

426
00:22:16,791 --> 00:22:20,125
The time for final redemption!

427
00:23:54,375 --> 00:23:56,125
[LELOUCH] How did the
Emperor bring me here?!

428
00:23:56,208 --> 00:23:58,458
Dammit, I have to
think this through!

429
00:23:58,541 --> 00:24:00,875
If he did this, he must
know that I'm Zero!

430
00:24:00,958 --> 00:24:03,416
So there's no reason
to hide it anymore!

431
00:24:03,500 --> 00:24:06,666
The best plan is to use my
Geass to make him my servant.

432
00:24:06,750 --> 00:24:10,458
Then I won't need to capture
V.V. and trade him for Nunnally.

433
00:24:10,541 --> 00:24:13,583
But his own Geass and
this place stand in my way!

434
00:24:13,666 --> 00:24:15,208
So what are my options?!

435
00:24:15,291 --> 00:24:16,916
It's all or nothing now!

436
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:20,541
This is a once in a lifetime
chance! I have to seize it!

